go back behind them walls.

01:29.357 --> 01:31.058
-Ooh, my baby is home.
-Hey, Ma.

01:31.091 --> 01:32.493
-(laughs)
-Thank God.

01:32.526 --> 01:34.228
-Ooh.
-Hey, Pop.

01:34.262 --> 01:36.430
-Son.
-Yes. Come on,
let's get out of here.

01:36.464 --> 01:37.831
-I know you hungry.
-Oh, yeah.

01:37.865 --> 01:39.167
-Boy, what you been doing?
-(Andre laughs)

01:39.200 --> 01:41.269
-(alarm buzzes)
-DIANA: You're back.

01:41.302 --> 01:43.671
