to say, Mr. MBA?

24:51.558 --> 24:52.692
(screaming)

24:55.427 --> 24:57.163
Where's the safe? Safe!

24:57.196 --> 24:59.398
-Behind the gold record!
-What's the combo?

24:59.431 --> 25:01.267
-3-2-1.
-Figures.

25:06.372 --> 25:08.040
This all you got?

25:08.074 --> 25:09.742
