of my damn money?!

25:09.776 --> 25:11.510
-I'll get you the rest, I swear.
-Do something.

25:14.513 --> 25:16.115
I'm coming back here, man.
I want my money.

25:22.589 --> 25:25.725
That's the money
pulled out of that safe.

25:25.758 --> 25:27.894
Now that's two grand,
and it'll get us through

25:27.927 --> 25:31.263
a hard time or two,
but at what cost?

25:31.297 --> 25:33.199
What you did in that office
was reckless.

25:33.232 --> 25:35.067
-I know what I'm doing.
-Do you?

25:35.101 --> 25:38.370
We will have no future, Pop,

25:38.404 --> 25:41.741
if we don't make it clear
to anybody, anybody

25:41.774 --> 25:44.677
