we will get what's ours.

25:44.711 --> 25:47.113
I'm the father!

25:47.146 --> 25:50.249
If somebody's got to risk
their life for this family,

25:50.282 --> 25:51.884
it's gonna be me.

25:51.918 --> 25:54.353
That's my job.

25:54.386 --> 25:56.022
Now, I know that
you went in there

25:56.055 --> 25:59.058
and you learned a few things,
but somehow along the way,

25:59.091 --> 26:01.360
when they took your name
and gave you a number,

26:01.393 --> 26:06.232
