in an alleyway?

26:16.175 --> 26:19.912
Now, I told you

26:19.946 --> 26:24.116
I'm the one that put
that fire in you.

26:24.150 --> 26:26.585
Let me show you
how to control it,

26:26.619 --> 26:28.655
how to hone it.

26:30.790 --> 26:32.692
Okay.

